[Were you Oh Soon-sang?]


32
00:01:26,410 --> 00:01:29,350
[Yes. I'm Oh Soon-sang.]


33
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:31,220
[My husband and actress Cha Do-yeong...]


34
00:01:31,289 --> 00:01:32,450
[The face of Wujeong Capital...]


35
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:33,960
[Locanda Jeju CEO, Nam Ji-seon.]


36
00:01:34,020 --> 00:01:35,190
[Check your email...]


37
00:01:35,259 --> 00:01:37,229
Why did you play this trick on me?


38
00:01:37,289 --> 00:01:38,860
[I need you to report]


39
00:01:38,930 --> 00:01:41,930
Song Yeo-wool's every move to me.


40
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:48,570
[So what did you find out?]


41
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:52,910
[Your relationship with Hwang Na-yoon.]


42
00:01:56,340 --> 00:01:58,750
There's no reason for me to stay here.


43
00:01:59,150 --> 00:02:01,320
[How much of what you said is true?]


44
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,920
-High five.
[-Danny Oh, a gym teacher...]


45
00:02:02,980 --> 00:02:04,220
What about Canada and ice hockey?


46
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:06,760
Even if you're a lowlife and a crook,


47
00:02:06,820 --> 00:02:09,259
[the students here believed
that you were a teacher.]


48
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:12,530
Didn't it make you feel guilty
or bother your conscience at all?


49
00:02:13,290 --> 00:02:15,130
[As you said, I'm a fake.]


50
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:18,000
[But not everything I did was fake.]


51
00:02:18,070 --> 00:02:21,100
[To you and Yi-chan.]


52
00:02:21,170 --> 00:02:22,240
-We can do it!
-We can do it!


53
00:02:24,370 --> 00:02:27,410
[No matter what I say,
it will all seem like an excuse,]


54
00:02:28,010 --> 00:02:32,010
[but if you need any help,
give me a call.]


55
00:02:45,130 --> 00:02:46,260
This guy, again?


56
00:02:46,329 --> 00:02:47,860
He's my legal representative.


57
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:50,300
Will you excuse us for a minute?


58
00:02:50,370 --> 00:02:51,570
I need to talk to him in private.


59
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,820
What's going on? Why are you here?


60
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:10,490
Mr. Oh Soon-sang. Listen carefully.


61
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:13,590
I'm about to give you a new task.


62
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:15,720
What? What are you talking about?


63
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:20,030
I need to get out of here.
I must get Yi-chan back.


64
00:03:20,430 --> 00:03:22,960
And you're the only person
who can help me.


65
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:25,930
So please accept the task.


66
00:03:36,540 --> 00:03:37,650
Yi-chan.


67
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,520
What are you doing out here?


68
00:03:43,220 --> 00:03:45,050
Auntie Na-yoon.


69
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,120
When is my mom coming back?


70
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:48,590
Tomorrow?


71
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:52,490
I'm not sure.


72
00:03:53,090 --> 00:03:55,730
Let's go to bed now
and wait for her tomorrow.


73
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,400
It's getting late.


74
00:03:57,670 --> 00:04:01,500
By the way,
can't you make up with my mom now?


75
00:04:02,370 --> 00:04:05,040
-What?
-You two had a fight, didn't you?


76
00:04:05,770 --> 00:04:09,180
The last time, my mom was
taken by the police afterward.


77
00:04:10,380 --> 00:04:13,750
Is that what happened this time too?


78
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,149
That's not it.


79
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:19,690
Then is it because of me?


80
00:04:21,089 --> 00:04:22,190
No.


81
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:26,130
It has nothing to do with me or you.


82
00:04:26,460 --> 00:04:28,530
The police need to ask your mom
a few questions.


83
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:30,700
And if Mom takes too long,


84
00:04:30,770 --> 00:04:33,430
you can live with me and Jae-in here.


85
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:35,940
I want to live with my mom.


86
00:04:38,210 --> 00:04:40,740
Okay. Let's go inside now.


87
00:04:40,810 --> 00:04:42,110
I'll tuck you in.


88
00:04:49,980 --> 00:04:54,320
[Holding Cell 1, Holding Cell 2]


89
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:02,030
He should be in bed by now.


90
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:07,470
Yi-chan.


91
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:20,080
[The police will start
searching my house tomorrow.]


92
00:05:21,380 --> 00:05:24,090
[There's something
I need you to remove before that.]


93
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:30,790
Is it here?


94
00:05:40,370 --> 00:05:41,400
What?


95
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:05,460
Including pill bottles,
drugs, and prescriptions,


96
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:07,360
search for any direct evidence.


97
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:08,630
-Get moving!
-Yes, sir.


