100
00:07:17,130 --> 00:07:18,830
[Doh Jin-sol, Nam Ji-seon]


101
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,940
[An Ji-yong,
Wujeong Capital, Cha Do-yeong]


102
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:27,710
[Money laundering?]


103
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:29,010
[Why did Midas Investment
and Locanda Hotel exchange money?]


104
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:30,340
[The relationship
between An Ji-yong and Nam Ji-seon?]


105
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:35,620
[Doh Jin-sol, Chairman of Jeju HSC]


106
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,790
[Nam Ji-seon, CEO of Locanda Hotel]


107
00:07:37,850 --> 00:07:39,320
[Chairman and parent?]


108
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,940
You'll be here for another 24 hours.


109
00:07:58,810 --> 00:08:01,280
-You should eat.
-I'm not hungry.


110
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:05,910
While searching your home,


111
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,780
I found something very interesting.


112
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:11,120
This tells me you're not over


113
00:08:09,250 --> 00:08:10,720
[Was An Ji-yong involved
in the establishment of the school?]


114
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:13,860
your husband, Mr. An Ji-yong's death yet.


115
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:16,690
What is it?
Was the late chairman Doh Jin-sol


116
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,860
involved with your husband?


117
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,700
According to Chairman Doh,


118
00:08:22,330 --> 00:08:24,600
my husband's funds
have been closely engaged


119
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:27,000
in the school foundation
since its establishment.


120
00:08:27,670 --> 00:08:29,740
The two of them seem to have known
each other well.


121
00:08:31,770 --> 00:08:33,070
Do you mean


122
00:08:33,140 --> 00:08:35,780
some of his funds were invested
in the school foundation?


123
00:08:38,350 --> 00:08:39,610
Look.


124
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:43,450
Until now, you've been claiming
that you have no motive.


125
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:46,550
But if your husband and the chairman
were involved with each other,


126
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:48,260
that changes everything.


127
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:54,430
Here, CEO Nam Ji-seon of Locanda Jeju
is mentioned.


128
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,830
[The relationship
between An Ji-yong and Nam Ji-seon?]


129
00:08:54,730 --> 00:08:56,930
How is she involved in this case?


130
00:08:57,430 --> 00:08:58,870
The day before the event,


131
00:08:59,530 --> 00:09:02,900
I overheard Ms. Nam
and the chairman arguing.


132
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:06,440
[How dare you bring up my kids
with that filthy mouth of yours?]


133
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:17,290
You'll regret what happened today.


134
00:09:20,420 --> 00:09:23,390
After the chairman passed away,
Ms. Nam asked me


135
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:26,260
to keep the incident
within the walls of the school.


136
00:09:27,730 --> 00:09:28,700
Why?


137
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:31,570
Ms. Nam has been wary of us
ever since we moved here.


138
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:34,370
I was aware that she had invested
in my husband's company,


139
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:36,600
but I didn't know any details.


140
00:09:37,370 --> 00:09:40,780
All I know is that my husband,
the late chairman, and Ms. Nam...


141
00:09:41,010 --> 00:09:42,610
The three of them were


142
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:45,710
involved with each other
one way or another.


143
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:50,080
There are four of you, not three.


144
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,650
Including you, Ms. Song Yeo-wool.


145
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:57,020
That's all I can tell you.


146
00:09:57,090 --> 00:10:00,430
Hear the rest from Ms. Nam directly.


147
00:10:12,070 --> 00:10:14,010
Search for any possible evidence,


148
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,540
even if it's a single strand of hair.


149
00:10:15,610 --> 00:10:17,310
I can't let that woman walk free.


150
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:18,380
Yes, sir.


151
00:10:19,010 --> 00:10:21,120
The police are searching her house today.


152
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,050
Are they looking for something?


153
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:28,460
Apparently, they have critical evidence
pointing to drug-induced homicide


154
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:29,960
and believe that she'll be found guilty.


155
00:10:30,060 --> 00:10:32,590
-"Drug-induced"?
-The drug found in Chairman Doh's body


156
00:10:32,660 --> 00:10:35,600
cannot be obtained without a prescription.


157
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:44,540
Get me another bottle.


158
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:45,870
You already drank quite a bit.


159
00:10:45,940 --> 00:10:47,380
Don't make me repeat myself


160
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:49,410
unless you're going to drink with me.


161
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:58,220
[Director Lee Jung-woo]


162
